1. View All Posts - http://localhost:8000/posts
2. Create a New Post - http://localhost:8000/posts/create
3. Store a New Post - http://localhost:8000/posts
4. View a Specific Post - http://localhost:8000/posts/1
5. Edit a Specific Post - http://localhost:8000/posts/1/edit
6. Update a Specific Post - http://localhost:8000/posts/1
7. Delete a Specific Post - http://localhost:8000/posts/1

////
Summary of URLs
List all posts: http://localhost:8000/posts
Create a new post: http://localhost:8000/posts/create
View a specific post: http://localhost:8000/posts/{id}
Edit a specific post: http://localhost:8000/posts/{id}/edit